item.title: CVE-2022-3882|2024-08-03T01:20:58.588Z -- unknown -- memory%20usage%2C%20memory%20limit%2C%20php%20and%20server%20memory%20health%20check%20and%20fix%20plugin
item.description: The Memory Usage, Memory Limit, PHP and Server Memory Health Check and Fix Plugin WordPress plugin before 2.46 does not have proper authorisation and CSRF in an AJAX action, allowing any authenticated users, such as subscriber to call it and install and activate arbitrary plugins from wordpress.org
